## Phase 1: Replace Browser Dialogs (17 files)

**Goal:** Replace all `alert()` / `confirm()` calls with proper toast or ConfirmDialog patterns.

**Files to Update:**

| File | Dialog Type | Replacement Strategy |
|------|-------------|----------------------|
| `src/components/ProviderSettings.tsx` | alert | toast.error/success |
| `src/pages/FormResponses.tsx` | alert/confirm | toast + ConfirmDialog |
| `src/pages/FormBuilder.tsx` | alert/confirm | toast + ConfirmDialog |
| `src/components/BulkActionsBar.tsx` | confirm | ConfirmDialog (danger) |
| `src/components/FormBuilder/FieldEditor.tsx` | alert | toast.error |
| `src/components/FormBuilder/DependentValidationEditor.tsx` | alert | toast.error |
| `src/components/TimeEntryList.tsx` | confirm | ConfirmDialog (danger) |
| `src/components/ConfirmDialog.tsx` | confirm (internal) | Keep (fallback) |
| `src/components/WidgetManager.tsx` | confirm | ConfirmDialog |
| `src/components/PresetManager.tsx` | alert/confirm | toast + ConfirmDialog |
| `src/components/FormBuilder/ConditionalRuleEditor.tsx` | alert | toast.error |
| `src/components/MemberSettings.tsx` | confirm | ConfirmDialog (danger) |
| `src/widgets/NotesEditor.tsx` | alert | toast.error |
| `src/widgets/Kanban/CardDetailPanel.tsx` | alert/confirm | toast + ConfirmDialog |
| `src/components/CustomFieldsSettings.tsx` | confirm | ConfirmDialog (danger) |
| `src/components/InvoiceBuilder.tsx` | alert | toast.success/error |
| `src/widgets/Automations/RuleBuilder.tsx` | alert | toast.error |

**Pattern:**
```tsx
// Before
alert('Task created');
if (confirm('Delete this item?')) { ... }

// After
import { toast } from '../stores/useToastStore';
toast.success('Task created');

// For destructive actions:
const [itemToDelete, setItemToDelete] = useState<Item | null>(null);
// ...
setItemToDelete(item);
// In render:
<ConfirmDialog
  isOpen={!!itemToDelete}
  onClose={() => setItemToDelete(null)}
  onConfirm={() => { deleteItem(itemToDelete.id); setItemToDelete(null); }}
  title="Delete Item"
  message="Are you sure you want to delete this item?"
  confirmLabel="Delete"
  variant="danger"
/>
```

